            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very good school,Principal and teachers are very good.  Good education is given to students.  Teacher are cordial end ensure students are doing good in all aspects. School Admin is very cordial and give all the required information to parents as and also when they require any information.  School fees is very nominal and affordable.  There is no pressure on students and parents.  Children can educate themselves well.  Overall it is very good.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
