          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I’m a parent of kids who were studying here for more that 5 yrs. the school is at its worst post covid.. very irregular teachers. The don’t even give extra coaching even for extremely weak students. So I applied TC for my kids. Thrice I came to this school reg TC. Every time they make us fill a form n us back. I’m a working woman n I took permission every time I came here n the staffs r so irresponsible.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
