            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Teachers are very friendly and cooperative.Extra curriculum activities are also given importance. Teachers are very cool in handling our children. Students are not squeezed to study instead they are given a chance to enhance their skills here. Able to see visible difference in behavior and academically also.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
